Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.61,0:21:04.99,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1\bord0.8\c&HFAE7FB&\3c&HBD36C2&\4c&HB75AC3&}奉献给你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:11.33,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1\bord0.8\c&HFAE7FB&\3c&HBD36C2&\4c&HB75AC3&}是时候与你说再见了
